quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  98,1,Ehl-e-kitab kay kafir aur mushrik log jabb tak kay unkay pass zahir daleel na ajaye baz rehnay waly na thay(who daleel yeh thi kay)
  98,2,Allah Taalaa ka aik rasol jo pak saheefay parhay
  98,3,jin mein sahi aur durust ehkam hon
  98,4,Ehl-e-kitab apnay pass zahir daleel ajanay kay baad hi (ikhtilaaf mein par ker) mutafarriq hogaey
  98,5,Unhein isskay siwa koi hokum nahi diya gaya kay sirf Allah ki ibadat kerein ussi kay liey deen ko khalis rakhein.ibraheem hanif kay deen per aur salat ko qaem rakhein aur zakat dety rahen yehi hai deen sedhi millat ka
  98,6,Be-shak jo log ehl-e-kitab mein say kafir huye aur mushrikeen sab dozakh ki aag mein(jaeigy)jahan who hamesha(hamesha)reheingy.yeh log bad tareen khalaeeq hain
  98,7,Be-shak jo log eman laey aur nek amal kiey yeh log behtreen khalaeeq hain
  98,8,Inn ka badla unkay rab kay pass hameshgi wohi jannaten hein jinkay neechy nehrein beh rahi hein jin mein who hamesha hamesha rahein gay.Allah Taalaa unsy razi hua aur yeh uss say razi huye.yeh hai uskay liey jo apnay perwardigar say daray